title: Chelone Miller: Mammoth Main Park
description:
Normally when it gets windy at Mammoth Mountain  riders run for cover or at least the comfort of the lodge and a warm drink at the bar. But, Arbor team rider Chelone “Chilly” Miller is a different breed… a windy day simply means an empty park to slay.

Ch
